### Using Forms

When submitting forms in the application:

1. Fill in all required fields (marked with *)
2. Review your input before submitting
3. If you encounter errors, check the error messages and correct your input

### Error Messages

If you encounter an error:

1. Read the error message carefully
2. Check that all required fields are filled
3. Verify that your input meets any specified requirements
4. Try the operation again
5. If the error persists, contact your administrator

## Tips and Tricks

1. Use the navigation menu to move between sections
2. Most lists can be sorted by clicking column headers
3. Use the search function when available to find specific items
4. Your browser's back button works throughout the application

